Nord theme (RTL): transparent circular favicons.

Identical change to freshrss-nord-favicons-ltr.patch, applied to the
right-to-left stylesheet. Split into a separate file so each stylesheet
can be applied, skipped, or detected as already-applied independently.

--- a/p/themes/Nord/nord.rtl.css
+++ b/p/themes/Nord/nord.rtl.css
@@ -471,8 +471,8 @@
 }

 img.favicon {
-	background: var(--text-accent);
-	border-radius: 4px;
+	background: none;
+	border-radius: 50%;
 }

